review: I have been visiting Dr Dabolkar for two years, since he fixed my teeth after two broke during a dengue rigor. He is extremely experienced, gives a lot of information, and his practice is friendly and professional. I have switched over from my UK dentist because of my satisfaction.

I came from Newyork to Mumbai to meet my friend Dr.Mukul and get some dentistry done, had a great time and he helped me a lot in my self-esteem and happiness. I am planning to come back in 2 years..for routine checkup and to meet Dr. Mukul and friends.
Wonderful Doctor with absolute clear line of perfects action. Painless process and zero hassle. Well trained staff
It was great. The doctors explained the issues very well and discussed probable solutions. Gave enough time.

Good service & professionalism 

Location is perfect 

Will visit again for advanced treatment 

Looking forward to the next visit
Doctor explaine issues verywell. Treatment was painless. Importantly, I was issued a bill and allowed to pay by credit card.
Dr communication and information sharing excellent. very experienced with the work he does every treatment is painless
Mukul is a very experienced doctor and professional in approach ...very happy with treatment. The stuff is friendly and helpful.
Great expertise in handling difficult procedure completed with good skills and care! Been with Dr.mukul for a long time.

I am visiting Dr. Dabholkar's clinic since 1989 for dental advice for me and my Ms. Shivpuri. He is outstanding in his job and he is availing latest techniques on dental treatment which is very satisfying the patients self esteem.
Best wishes.
